---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Nos Services" 
  description="Découvrez nos services professionnels de plomberie, débouchage et chauffage à Bruxelles."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1>Nos Services</h1>
      <p>Des solutions sur mesure pour tous vos besoins en plomberie</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section" id="plomberie">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail-grid">
        <div class="service-image-box glass-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585704032915-c3400ca199e7?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Plomberie Générale" class="service-img" />
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><path d="M12 10a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Plomberie Générale</h2>
          <p>Nous prenons en charge tous vos travaux de plomberie, de la simple réparation de fuite à l'installation complète de votre salle de bain.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Recherche et réparation de fuites
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Installation de sanitaires et robinetterie
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Remplacement de chauffe-eau
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Rénovation de salle de bain
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">Demander un devis</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light" id="debouchage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail-grid reverse">
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m16 12-4-4-4 4"/><path d="M12 16V8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Débouchage Professionnel</h2>
          <p>Une canalisation bouchée peut causer de nombreux désagréments. Notre équipe intervient rapidement avec le matériel adéquat pour résoudre votre problème.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Débouchage WC et éviers
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Débouchage haute pression des égouts
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Inspection par caméra (endoscopie)
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Curage de canalisations
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">Intervention urgente</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-image-box glass-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905252507-b35492cc74b4?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Débouchage professionnel" class="service-img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="chauffage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail-grid">
        <div class="service-image-box glass-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504328345606-18bbc8c9d7d1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Chauffage et Chaudière" class="service-img" />
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"/><path d="m17 5-5-3-5 3"/><path d="m17 19-5 3-5-3"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="m5 7 3 5-3 5"/><path d="m19 7-3 5 3 5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Chauffage</h2>
          <p>Nous assurons l'installation, l'entretien et la réparation de vos systèmes de chauffage pour garantir votre confort thermique tout au long de l'année.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Entretien de chaudières
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Dépannage chauffage
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Installation de radiateurs
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Purge et désembouage
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">Prendre rendez-vous</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .service-detail-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .service-detail-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    
    .service-detail-grid.reverse .service-content {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  .service-image-box {
    padding: 1rem;
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .service-image-box:hover {
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }

  .service-img {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .icon-box {
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .mt-4 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
